==English==

===Etymology===
Old French ''[[propinquité]]'' or Latin ''[[propinquitas]]'', from ''[[propinquus]]'' ‘neighbouring’ (from ''[[prope]]'' ‘near’).

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/prə'pɪŋkwɪti/}}

===Noun===
